net.proteusframework.core

Class ToStringComparator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.ToStringComparator<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - object type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparator<T>

    public class ToStringComparator<T>
extends Object
implements Comparator<T>
    Does a comparison on Object.toString(). This class is meant to be used in conjunction with Collections.sort.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
